{"word":"H4605 - מַעַל - maʻal - mah'al - Above","slug":"H4605","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מַעַל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>maʻal"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mah'al"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Above"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E2;&#x05DC; - ma&#x201B;al</b> - <i>mah'-al</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H5927\">H5927</a>; properly the <i>upper</i> part, used only adverbially with prefix <i>upward</i>, <i>above</i>, <i>overhead</i>, <i>from the top</i>, etc.: - above, exceeding (-ly), forward, on (X very) high, over, up (-on, -ward), very."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H131\">H131</a>, <a href=\"#/H4607\">H4607</a>, <a href=\"#/H4608\">H4608</a>, <a href=\"#/H4609\">H4609</a>, <a href=\"#/H4610\">H4610</a>, <a href=\"#/H5920\">H5920</a>, <a href=\"#/H5921\">H5921</a>, <a href=\"#/H5927\">H5927</a>, <a href=\"#/H5929\">H5929</a>, <a href=\"#/H5930\">H5930</a>, <a href=\"#/H5933\">H5933</a>, <a href=\"#/H5935\">H5935</a>, <a href=\"#/H5940\">H5940</a>, <a href=\"#/H5941\">H5941</a>, <a href=\"#/H5942\">H5942</a>, <a href=\"#/H5944\">H5944</a>, <a href=\"#/H5945\">H5945</a>, <a href=\"#/H8585\">H8585</a>"}]}